{"title":"Restrap Tire Boot Kit offers a super light, permanent patch for cut tires","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/13/restrap-tire-boot-kit-offers-a-super-light-permanent-patch-for-cut-tires/","date":1631562856000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"567\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154319/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-6-e1631562235752-800x567.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs%3Adevice%2Frscb28-1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-271368\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>We’ve all been there. Stranded on the side of the road with a cut tire, forced to improvise a tire boot with whatever is close at hand. Maybe that’s a dollar bill, or an empty Gu packet… really, just anything flat and durable enough to keep your tube inside the tire for the ride home. For those that want something a little more permanent though, Restrap is offering a simple kit that looks perfect for the job.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Tire Boot Kit \" width=\"1182\" height=\"564\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624.jpg 1182w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-297x142.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-800x382.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-120x57.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-768x366.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1182px) 100vw, 1182px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624.jpg 1182w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-297x142.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-800x382.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-120x57.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154307/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-1-e1631562429624-768x366.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>Simply called their Tire (or Tyre) Boot Kit, the whole it is basically one roll of very light and durable Hyplalon fabric. There are eight pre-cut boot shapes held in place with a few easily breakable bonds, in different shapes to work for different type tears.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13154312/REstrap-tire-boot-kit-3.jpg\"><img load